author: USA TODAY, Bart Jansen, USA TODAY
title: Pennsylvania protest latest, largest among rallies nationwide urging end to coronavirus restrictions
description: About 2,000 people honked and jeered against coronavirus restrictions Monday in Harrisburg, Pa., the latest in a growing movement against shutdowns.
content:
Multiple states across the country have seen protests as stay-at-home orders meant to curb the spread of the coronavirus continue.
